The Bureau can take its
toll on your family.

218
00:15:50,836 --> 00:15:53,933
I understand that.
My ex-wife is a...

219
00:15:54,496 --> 00:15:56,551
an agent and, um...

220
00:15:57,437 --> 00:15:59,643
let's just say I
know how you feel.

221
00:16:01,775 --> 00:16:06,051
Promise me that he
won't find out we spoke?

222
00:16:06,705 --> 00:16:09,052
Oh, it's totally confidential.

223
00:16:09,197 --> 00:16:10,880
Do you mind if I ask why?

224
00:16:11,026 --> 00:16:14,123
To be perfectly honest,
he scares me.

225
00:16:49,105 --> 00:16:50,041
Information.

226
00:16:50,186 --> 00:16:52,631
Hi, I need the number for
a Sundown Hotel please.

227
00:16:52,768 --> 00:16:54,562
- What state?
- Uh, all of them, please.

228
00:16:54,596 --> 00:16:56,653
- Got one in Pierre, South Dakota.
- Okay.

229
00:16:56,797 --> 00:16:58,722
Another in Sutton,
West Virginia

230
00:16:58,815 --> 00:17:01,160
and one more in Gila,
New Mexico.

231
00:17:37,276 --> 00:17:40,321
- What can I do you for?
- A batch of them sunflowers, please.

232
00:17:40,416 --> 00:17:43,862
You don't mind me saying, you do
not sound like you hail from Kansas.

233
00:17:43,985 --> 00:17:45,532
You've got a sharp ear.

234
00:17:45,678 --> 00:17:49,953
I hail from what we call the,
uh, Yellowhammer State.

235
00:17:50,147 --> 00:17:52,160
What brings you to Tribune?

236
00:17:58,497 --> 00:17:59,291
Sir?

237
00:18:01,046 --> 00:18:02,541
Romance.

238
00:18:05,508 --> 00:18:07,241
Thank you so much.

239
00:18:13,486 --> 00:18:15,451
Somebody's going to get hurt.

240
00:18:15,735 --> 00:18:18,002
Feds going to be swinging
bigger bats than these.

241
00:18:18,037 --> 00:18:19,150
We gotta have ours.

242
00:18:19,347 --> 00:18:22,442
Look, man, that's all we need
is your car, your truck,

243
00:18:22,586 --> 00:18:25,310
and some guts, man.
We don't need all of this.

244
00:18:25,456 --> 00:18:27,990
- Maybe we should think about it.
- I said no!

